job.title: Indian Air Force Recruitment 2021 – 85 Group C Civilian Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:85

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Group C Civilian.

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for matric pass has been published by Indian Air Force for Group C Civilian. vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Group C Civilian., from 30-07-2021, and till 30-08-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Group C Civilian. in the Indian Air Force, your 10th.12th class must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 30-07-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 30-08-2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

Indian Air Force Group C Civilian. Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

Detailed vacancies:

How to apply for Indian Air Force Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Group C Civilian. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of the Indian Air Force and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by Indian Air Force
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
